## Validated Findings
1. Bridge real-runtime path is not implemented (returns 501).
2. Invoke route in infra does not match OpenAPI contract.
3. SigV4 machine auth path remains stubbed and denies all.
4. Request interceptor file is docstring-only (no handler).
5. Response interceptor file is docstring-only (no handler).
6. BFF handler file is docstring-only (no handler).
7. Bridge role-ARN naming does not match TenantStack role naming.
8. Job isolation model allows weak tenant boundary enforcement via JOB# access pattern.
9. Async job polling/webhook path is only partially implemented (tracked by open Phase 8 issues).

