- #91 (new): Align invoke route with OpenAPI contract
- #92 (new): Fix tenant execution role ARN contract mismatch
- #93 (new): Harden tenant isolation for job access paths

## Queue Labeling Rule
Use queue-managed labels only:
- phase:*
- status:not-started | status:in-progress | status:done | status:blocked
- type:task
- ready

No additional ad-hoc labels should be applied to queued implementation issues.
